snippet.title: Paddle Games - VC4000
snippet.description: A quick look at the 60 different pong variants in this game. The analog joysticks gives us two axis gameplay. The breakout clone game mode "Whipe-Out" is the most fun. There are 12 main modes and a total of 60 With all difficutly settings. Blogpost: http://retro-spill.blogspot.com/2013/11/paddle-games-3-vc-4000.html
